the last ones shall be first ( german : die &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; die &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; ) is a 1957 west german crime film directed by rolf hansen , based on the short play the first and the last by john galsworthy . it was entered into the 7th berlin international film festival .